What does #COVID19 Antibody ”+” Mean? @JAMAInternalMed
 
N=3.2M people. 12% were + for #COVID AB. Seropositivity appeared protective from future infection. Duration of protection is unknown & #Vaccine is recommended REGARDLESS of AB status.
